name: Buenas
description:
an intro to my kitchen, but most importantly to my very loud companion that you may hear purring in the back. Like many before me, I've found my kitchen to be a comforting environment in which not only I can eat my feelings away but, also a medium to express myself artistically. I hope to create a space that feels as creative, exciting, and mouthwatering as it feels in my mind when I'm cooking. Of course, there is more to my relationship with food than my eternal quest for the perfect bite, but I digress. Welcome.

P.S. my pronouns are they/them
